# ORIG TITLE    Italy’s PDL thanks Berlusconi for his ‘faith in success’ . 
# ORIG CONTENT  The People of Freedom party (PDL) . is pleased with the centre-right’s strong performance in Italy’s parliamentary elections, Feburary 24-25. Controversial former prime minister Silvio Berlusconi, the founder and president of the party, made a dramatic return to political stage during the campaign. The People of Freedom’s Secretary General Angelino Alfano thanked him, saying, “I talked with President Berlusconi to thank him in the name of the PDL for this extraordinary result, which we owe to his tenacity, his generous force and his faith in success”. 
